@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_agbaxx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.79
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.55) - (wp.cos(v1 + 0.56) - wp.sin(v2 + 0.97)))
    tmp = ((v0 / (v0 + 0.70 + v2 + 0.36)) + ((v2 + 0.22 - v1 + 0.98) - v2))
    tmp = 0.34
    v0 = (v0 + (tmp / (v1 + 0.85 / v0 + 0.98)))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.abs((v0 + 0.75 / v0 + 0.62)))
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.cos(v2 + 0.29) + 0.46))
    data[tid] = v0
